= c_{+}' (1-y - z) \tag{3.6.14}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚
ãã—ã¦(3.6.10)å¼ã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[\frac{N_\mathrm{He^{++}} (N_\mathrm{He^{+}} + 2 N_\mathrm{He^{++}})}{N_\mathrm{He^{+}}} 
